parameters:
General Tros "Well... Swordsman Leader Kru... Not a single one of the
renowned experts who went to investigate the Holy Forest has returned. As
the person in charge, how do you perceive this?"

Kru "Sir! I believe it is entirely due to my lack of proper recognition of
the situation."
General Tros "Hmm. And what measures do you intend to take?"

Kru "Sir! I myself will go and will surely find the altar of the god
Xecelray."
General Tros "Hmm... I shall await your good report then."
Kru "...May I ask a question?"
シフ1
Chancellor Shif "No... It seems you do not understand your place."
Kru "My apologies!"
シフ4

Chancellor Shif "For someone of your lowly birth and vile status to be
granted life in the presence of the king, you are already receiving an
extraordinary honor. And yet, you dare to ask a question..."
King "Mumble mumble..."
シフ3

Chancellor Shif "Sir... Understood. Hey, commoner... The king has given his
permission. Let's hear this question that comes from your inferior mind."

Kru "Sir! I am most grateful. We have made many sacrifices so far, but what
value does the altar of the god Xecelray hold?"
シフ5
Chancellor Shif "Hmph! You don't even know that!"

General Tros "It's fine. Let me explain. According to legend, the god
Xecelray is said to possess the power to grant humans eternal youth and
immortality. The king believes it is necessary to obtain this power of
eternal life."
Kru "I see. Such power..."
King "Mumble mumble..."
シフ8

Chancellor Shif "...Sir. Hey, commoner! The conversation is over! Step back
immediately!"
Kru "Sir! Understood."
